cars.description: This is an immaculate 2006 Nissan Rogue with only 25000 miles on it. Leather seats, power everything.
Its got most of its tires.
The toy you've always dreamed of. Plastic everything. No motor.
This thing is outta time. Can't drive over 88 mph
In my Subaru with the Kombucha mushroom people, sitting around all day.
Its got 4 tires and its a truck, the end.
Its red like on your poster, pew pew pew.
This thing is half car, half truck, half pickle. Wat.
